N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 105.23 - Reimbursements by uninsured accident and health plans

State Regulations

Report as a negative amount: administrative fees, direct reimbursement of expenses, or other similar receipts or credits attributable to uninsured accident and health plans and the uninsured portion of partially insured accident and health plans. Notes
